  {
    "name": "HOME_PARAGRAPH",
    "value": "<p> Book a sign language appointment with our expert team and access professional interpreting and Video Relay Services (VRS) designed to support clear and accessible communication. We work with individuals, businesses, and organisations to provide reliable sign language support across a wide range of settings, including healthcare, education, and the workplace. </p>  <p> Our qualified interpreters ensure accurate and effective communication, whether in person or through secure video relay technology. We understand the importance of accessibility and inclusion, which is why we offer flexible solutions tailored to your needs. </p>  <p> With a simple booking process and responsive support team, it’s easy to arrange the right service at the right time. Get started today and make communication accessible for everyone. </p>",
    "slotSetting": true
  },
  {
    "name": "HOME_POLICY",
    "value": "<div class=\"vrs-container\">     <div class=\"vrs-card\">         <h3>To use our VRS, you must:</h3>         <ul>             <li>Be a member of the InSignLanguage Career Network</li>             <li>Complete our onboarding process</li>             <li> Agree to our Terms & Conditions: <a                     href=\"https://www.insignlanguage.co.uk/terms-and-conditions/fulllist\" target=\"_blank\"> Full list                     here </a> </li>         </ul>     </div>     <div class=\"vrs-card\">         <h3>📅 Booking a VRS Call</h3>         <ul>             <li>You can book a session once onboarding is complete</li>             <li>Interpreters cannot be assigned until onboarding is finished</li>             <li>All bookings must go through the official link or app</li>             <li>Availability may vary</li>         </ul>     </div>     <div class=\"vrs-card\">         <h3>🎦 Using the Service</h3>         <ul>             <li> Use the VRS link: <a href=\"https://videorelayservice.azurewebsites.net/\" target=\"_blank\">Open VRS Service </a> </li>             <li>Use the service respectfully and for appropriate purposes</li>             <li>Follow interpreter guidance during the call</li>             <li>Avoid misuse, inappropriate content, or unsafe communication</li>         </ul>     </div>     <div class=\"vrs-card\">         <h3>💬 Need Help?</h3>         <ul>             <li>Check our Terms & Conditions</li>             <li>Ask the AI helper on our website</li>             <li>Contact our team anytime</li>         </ul>     </div>     <div class=\"vrs-footer\"> We’re here to make your experience smooth, accessible, and stress-free. 💛 </div> </div>",
    "slotSetting": true
  },
